en_4439030_0	Colombo (News1st) – 27 suspects who have been arrested in connection with the recent violence in the Kandy area have been further remanded till the 14th of this month.
en_4439030_1	The suspects were remanded once again after being produced before the Theldeniya Magistrate.
en_4439030_2	Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna (SLPP) candidate Samantha Perera who was elected to the Kundasale Pradeshiya Sabah is among the suspects who were remanded once again.
en_4439030_3	The Magistrate ordered that the PS member be allowed to attend the PS session scheduled for the 9th of this month under the protective custody of Prison officials.
